snippet: The Supreme Court is poised to deliver its verdict in a case that weighs the religious rights of employers and the right of women to the birth control of their choice....

headline.print_headline: High Court Poised to Decide Birth-Control Dispute
headline.main: High Court Poised to Decide Birth-Control Dispute

lead_paragraph: The Supreme Court is poised to deliver its verdict in a case that weighs the religious rights of employers and the right of women to the birth control of their choice.
